column5: G'day Everyone,  Just a quick one - Anyone know what happened to the Bait & Tackle shop that was at the corner of HWY 89 and HWY 11?  I've searched online, and found that they're closed? Just wondering if anyone else has any updated information? I'm hoping they've either re-located or are still at that location?  Here's that link I found...  http://www.lakesimcoemessageboard.com/forums/index.php?topic=11275.0  Thanks all and tight lines!
Closed for the season. They were open,no minnows now.Same people,just around  back.Thinking they will open by the time Pike season opens

well they are still at the same location but at the back of the building  if they have closed again very recently,I had not herd but they were opened after the rebuild and the added gas station that is making the expensive esso across the street lower their gas prices
